msgid ""
"Automatic lowercasing of file extensions has been turned off.\n"
"\n"
"The Proton CLI now detects the media type correctly even when the extension "
"is uppercase, so renaming your local files is no longer needed.\n"
"\n"
"You can turn it back on in Configuration if you prefer your extensions "
"normalised anyway, or to repair older uploads that were sent with an "
"uppercase extension. Your choice will be kept."
